  "texts": [
    "We tested whether DEEPOMICS FFPE can classify variants with 1%-5% MAFs (\"Low MAF variants\" for DEEPOMICS FFPE in Table 1).",
    "DEEPOMIC FFPE removed artifacts with a specificity of 0.995 and preserved true variants with a sensitivity of 0.25.",
    "By contrast, MuTect filter removed only 7.5% of the artifacts (\"Low MAF variants\" for MuTect filter in Table 1).",
    "Consequently, 0.111% of the true variants remained among the predicted variants.",
    "Similar to DEEPOMICS FFPE, FFPolish successfully eliminated 98.8% of the FFPE-artifacts (\"Low MAF variants\" for FFPolish in Table 1)."
  ],
